4602,Hazrat Ata bin Yasar sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney soney ya chaandi ka eik bartan uskey wazan sey ziyada soney ya chaandi key iwaz kharid . Hazrat Abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko us jaisey sodey sey mana farmatey suna illa ye ke dono ka wazan barabar ho.
4603,Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey khaibar key din eik haar baara deenar ka kharid jis mein soney key ilawa moti aur mankey bhi they. jab mainey soney aur moti mankon ko alag alag kya to us sey baara deenar sey zayed sona nikal aaya. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : is qism ki chiz ko na bechaa jaey yahan tak ke soney waghera ko alag alag kar liya jaey.
4604,Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey khaibar key din eik haar baara deenar ka kharid jis mein soney key ilawa moti aur mankey bhi they. jab mainey soney aur moti mankon ko alag alag kya to us sey baara deenar sey zayed sona nikal aaya. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : is qism ki chiz ko na bechaa jaey yahan tak ke soney waghera ko alag alag kar liya jaey.
