4606,Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jang khaibar key din mujhey eik aisa haar mila jis mein soney key ilawa moti aur mankey bhi they. mainey usey bechney ka irada kya. ye baat Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey zikr ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : uskey hissey alag alag kar key bech .
4607,"Hazrat abu-Minhaal sey riwayat hai ke merey eik shareek ney chaandi ka soda udhaar kar liya, phir wo merey paas aaya aur mujhey bataya . mainey kaha : ye to durust nahin. wo kehney laga : Allah ki qism ! mainey ye soda bazar mein kya hai aur kisi ney bhi is par aetraz nahin kya. mein Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan Madina Munawra tashrif laye to hum is qism key sodey kya kartey they. aap ney farmaya : jo ( kharid o farokht ) naqad ho, is mein koi harj nahin aur jo udhaar ho, wo sood hai. phir unhoney mujhey kaha : Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey ja kar poochho. main unkey paas gaya aur puchha to unhoney bhi isi tarah farmaya."
