4621,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main baqee mein oonton ka karobar kya karta tha. ( kabhi ) soda diinaaron sey karta to dirham wasul kar leta tha. main (apni behan) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) key ghar mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! main aap sey poochhna chahta hun ke main Baqee mein oonton ka soda karta hun. soda dinaaron sey karta hun aur un ki jagah dirham wasul kar leta hun. aap ney farmaya is din key bhaaw key mutabiq ho to koi harj nahin, b-sharte-ke eik dusrey sey juda hotey waqt koi len-den baqi na ho."
