4672,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein log tijarati qaflon sey ghalla khareedtey they. aap ney unhein mana farmaya ke usi jagah usey farokht karen jahan wo kharid gaya tha yahan tak ke wo usey ghalla mandi mein muntaqil kar lein.
4673,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mubarak daur mein dekha ke jo log maapey baghair ghalla kharid kar wahin bech detey they, in ko (sarkari ummal (governer) ki taraf sey) saza di jati thi yahan tak ke wo usey apni dukanon par ley jaeyn."
4674,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mubarak daur mein dekha ke jo log maapey baghair ghalla kharid kar wahin bech detey they, in ko (sarkari ummal (governer) ki taraf sey) saza di jati thi yahan tak ke wo usey apni dukanon par ley jaeyn."
4675,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi sey ghalla udhaar kharid aur apni zireh uskey paas girwi rakhi.
