4677,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jo ki roti aur baasi charbi ley kar gaey. aap ki haalat ye thi ke aap ney Madina Munawra main eik Yahudi key paas apni zireh girwi rakhi hui thi kyonkey aap ney apney ghar walon key liye us sey kuch jo liye they.
4678,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas jo ki roti aur baasi charbi ley kar gaey. aap ki haalat ye thi ke aap ney Madina Munawra main eik Yahudi key paas apni zireh girwi rakhi hui thi kyonkey aap ney apney ghar walon key liye us sey kuch jo liye they.
4679,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik dusrey sey mashroot ) qarz aur bai jayez nahin. aur bai mein do shartein jayez nahin aur jo chiz terey paas nahin, uski bai bhi jayez nahin."
4680,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik dusrey sey mashroot ) qarz aur bai jayez nahin. aur bai mein do shartein jayez nahin aur jo chiz terey paas nahin, uski bai bhi jayez nahin."
4681,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi jis chiz ka Malik nahin, uski bai nahin kar sakta."
4682,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi jis chiz ka Malik nahin, uski bai nahin kar sakta."
4683,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas eik aadmi aata hai aur mujh sey aisi chiz bechney ka mutalba karta hai jo merey paas nahin hoti. main us sey us ka soda kar leta hun, phir main usey bazar sey kharidkar la deta hun. aap ney farmaya : jo chiz terey paas nahin, us ka soda na kar."
4684,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas eik aadmi aata hai aur mujh sey aisi chiz bechney ka mutalba karta hai jo merey paas nahin hoti. main us sey us ka soda kar leta hun, phir main usey bazar sey kharidkar la deta hun. aap ney farmaya : jo chiz terey paas nahin, us ka soda na kar."
4685,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Majalid sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat ibne Abi Oofa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bai (sauda) salaf (ya salam) key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key zamaney mein gehun, jau aur khajoor mein aisey logon key sath bai (sauda) salaf kiya kartey they jinkey mutalliq mujhey ilm nahin hota tha ke unkey paas (ghalla ya zameen) hai ya nahin. Hazrat ibne Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi aisey hi farmaya."
4686,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Majalid sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat ibne Abi Oofa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bai (sauda) salaf (ya salam) key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key zamaney mein gehun, jau aur khajoor mein aisey logon key sath bai (sauda) salaf kiya kartey they jinkey mutalliq mujhey ilm nahin hota tha ke unkey paas (ghalla ya zameen) hai ya nahin. Hazrat ibne Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi aisey hi farmaya."
4687,"Hazrat ibne Abi Majaalid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Barda aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaddad ka bai (sauda) salam ki baabat ikhtilaf ho gaya. unhoney mujhey Hazrat ibne Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja. mainey un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key zamaney mein gehun, jo , munaqqa aur khajuron mein aisey logon sey bai salam kiya kartey they jinkey paas hamarey khayal key mutabiq ye cheezen nahin hoti thin, phir mainey Hazrat ibne Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney bhi aisa hi farmaya."
4688,"Hazrat ibne Abi Majaalid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Barda aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaddad ka bai (sauda) salam ki baabat ikhtilaf ho gaya. unhoney mujhey Hazrat ibne Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja. mainey un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Hazrat Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma key zamaney mein gehun, jo , munaqqa aur khajuron mein aisey logon sey bai salam kiya kartey they jinkey paas hamarey khayal key mutabiq ye cheezen nahin hoti thin, phir mainey Hazrat ibne Abzaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha to unhoney bhi aisa hi farmaya."
4689,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye aur wo (log) do do, teen teen saal key liye khajuron mein bai (sauda) salaf kiya kartey they. aap ney in ko rok diya aur farmaya : jo shakhs bai salaf karey to wo moayan (tai-shuda) maap ya moayan wazan mein moayan muddat tak key liye kerey."
4690,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra tashrif laye aur wo (log) do do, teen teen saal key liye khajuron mein bai (sauda) salaf kiya kartey they. aap ney in ko rok diya aur farmaya : jo shakhs bai salaf karey to wo moayan (tai-shuda) maap ya moayan wazan mein moayan muddat tak key liye kerey."
4691,"Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey eik jawan oont qarz liya. wo shakhs aap sey apney oont ki wapsi ka mutalba karney aaya. aap ney eik aadmi sey kaha : jaao , us ko eik jawan oont kharid do. wo wapis aa kar kehney laga : mujhey to rubaai oont mil raha hai jo uskey oont sey bahut behtar hai. aap ney farmaya : yehi dey do. behtareen musalman wo hai jo (qarz waghera ki) adaegi mein achchhaa ho."
4692,"Hazrat Abu-Raafea' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey eik jawan oont qarz liya. wo shakhs aap sey apney oont ki wapsi ka mutalba karney aaya. aap ney eik aadmi sey kaha : jaao , us ko eik jawan oont kharid do. wo wapis aa kar kehney laga : mujhey to rubaai oont mil raha hai jo uskey oont sey bahut behtar hai. aap ney farmaya : yehi dey do. behtareen musalman wo hai jo (qarz waghera ki) adaegi mein achchhaa ho."
4693,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik shakhs ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik khas umr ka oont wapis lena tha. wo leney aaya to aap ney farmaya is ko dey do. logon ney talash kiya to uskey oont sey badi umr ka oont mila. aap ney farmaya : yehi dey do. us ney (bator shukr) kaha : aap ney mujhey ziyada dey diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen log wo hain jo (doosron key huquq ki) adaegi mein achchhey hon.
4694,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik shakhs ney Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik khas umr ka oont wapis lena tha. wo leney aaya to aap ney farmaya is ko dey do. logon ney talash kiya to uskey oont sey badi umr ka oont mila. aap ney farmaya : yehi dey do. us ney (bator shukr) kaha : aap ney mujhey ziyada dey diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen log wo hain jo (doosron key huquq ki) adaegi mein achchhey hon.
4695,Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariyaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik jawan oont diya tha. main uski adaegi key silsiley mein aap key paas hazir huwa to aap ney farmaya : haan. zarur main tujhey uski jagah eik (behtareen) bakhti oontni dunga. phir aap ney mujhey wo di aur bahut achchhi di. isi tarah aap key paas eik erabi (dehati) apna eik khas umr ka oont leney aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is ko koi oont dey do. logon ney us ko puri umr ka oont dey diya. wo erabi (dehati) kehney laga : ye to merey oont sey bahut behtar hai. aap ney farmaya : tum mein sey behtareen shakhs wo hai jo adaegi mein behtareen hai.
