4698,Hazrat Samrua bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney haiwaan key badley haiwaan ki udhaar bai (saudey) sey mana farmaya.
4699,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik ghulam aaya aur us ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey hijrat par baiat ki. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye ilm nahin tha ke wo ghulam hai. itney mein us ka Malik usey leney aa gaya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye mujhey bech dey. aap ney do kaley ghulam dey kar usey kharid liya. uskey baad aap ney kisi sey baiat nahin li yahan tak ke poochh letey ke wo ghulam to nahin.
