4707,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (jablal habla) (hamal key hamal) ki bai (saudey) sey mana farmaya aur ye eik qisam ki bai (sauda) thi jo jahiliyat waley aapas mein kartey they. koi aadmi oontni khareedtaa ke iski qeemat us waqt dunga jab ye oontni (maada) bachcha janey aur phir uskey pet wali oontni (badi ho kar) bachcha janey.
